    "details": {
      "biography": {
        "value": "<p>Grave-wisps are the remnant spirits of those who died in Svellheim's bitter winters — their souls too thin and cold to pass on, instead lingering as drifting motes of pale light. They are drawn to the living by an empty hunger, using their ghostly Lure to pull victims toward them before draining warmth with a Cold Touch. Incorporeal and nearly silent, they drift through walls and barriers, making them particularly terrifying in confined spaces.</p>",
